text: The Austrian Landesliga is the fourth level of football in Austria. It is divided into nine leagues— one for each Austrian state: *Burgenland: Landesliga Burgenland *Lower Austria: 1. Niederösterreichische Landesliga *Vienna: Wiener Stadtliga *Carinthia and East Tyrol: Kärntner Liga *Upper Austria: OÖ Liga *Styria: Landesliga Steiermark *Salzburg: Salzburger Liga *Tyrol (without East Tyrol): Tiroler Liga *Vorarlberg: Vorarlbergliga ==Other websites== *Landesliga Lower Austria *Landesliga Vienna *The Austrian Landesliga on soccerway.com *The Austrian Landesligas on Weltfussball.de 4
title: Austrian Landesliga
